PORT=3001
JWT_SECRET=your-secret-change-in-production
CORS_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8080

# ━━━ Supabase (권장: 영구 저장) ━━━
# Vercel/Render 변수 이름은 반드시 아래와 동일하게 (SUPABASE_ 접두사):
# SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...   # 서버 전용, anon 키가 아님
# SUPABASE_BANNERS_BUCKET=banners
#
# Main + /public/latest + /home use public.articles only (not articles_list_slim).
#
# 로컬 개발 전용: 기사·사용자를 JSON 파일로만 쓸 때 (운영 NODE_ENV=production·RENDER 에서는 무시됨):
# NW_DEV_LEGACY_FILE_DB=1

# ━━━ 재배포 후에도 기사·광고·업로드이미지·사용자를 유지하려면 (Render Persistent Disk 등) ━━━
# 디스크를 예: /data 에 마운트한 뒤 아래를 모두 설정하는 것을 권장합니다.
# 미설정 시 backend/data · backend/uploads 에 저장되며, 컨테이너 재시작·재배포마다 초기화됩니다.
#
# NW_ARTICLES_JSON_PATH=/data/articles.json
# NW_ADS_JSON_PATH=/data/ads.json
# NW_USERS_JSON_PATH=/data/users.json
# NW_UPLOADS_ROOT=/data/uploads
#
# 운영에서 기본 경로 사용 시 콘솔 경고를 강제하려면:
# NW_PERSISTENCE_WARN=1

# Main public API (/public/latest, /home/headlines): bounded public.articles table only (never articles_list_slim).
#
# 통합 피드 메모리 캐시만 우회(진단용). 메인 슬림과 별개.
# NW_UNIFIED_FEED_CACHE_BYPASS=1
#
# Public read soft-fail when Supabase is slow (default on; set NW_PUBLIC_READ_SOFT_FAIL=0 to disable).
# NW_PUBLIC_READ_SOFT_FAIL=1
# Read deadline for public routes (ms), 2000-120000. Stabilization: often 3000–5000; default 5000.
# NW_SUPABASE_READ_DEADLINE_MS=5000
# Max age of stale snapshot on failure (ms), 60000-3600000, default 180000 (3 min).
# NW_PUBLIC_SOFT_FAIL_STALE_MS=180000
#
# --- Supabase instability / usage (dashboard checklist) ---
# - Logs & API: 5xx, PostgREST timeouts, statement timeout; correlate with request id from backend logs.
# - Database: pooler vs direct; max connections; optional statement_timeout tuning on heavy queries.
# - Plan/usage: quota, read/write limits; elevated latency under load.
# Main first paint stays on public.articles bounded reads; /api/home and /popular use soft-fail (200 partial or []).
#
# =============================================================================
# Fixed policy: main resilience vs Supabase flake (do not regress without review)
# =============================================================================
# 1) Center cause is often Supabase limits / timeouts / cache / 522. App changes only
#    to tolerate flake: deadlines, soft-fail, partial JSON, client preserve-hero (not "fix DB" in Node).
# 2) Main first paint: public.articles bounded reads ONLY. No articles_list_slim; no unified-feed
#    merge on /public/latest, /home/headlines, or /api/home latest slice (see articles.supabase.js).
# 3) /api/home, /api/articles/public/popular, deferred latest?limit=25: keep soft-fail (200 + degraded/partial/[]).
# 4) Ads / popular / bundle failures: degrade side widgets only; do not clear hero article text
#    (script.js: nwMainUiPreserveHeroOnEmptyApply, nwApplyMainFromHomePayload skips empty latest).
# 5) Hero image quality, storage, body merge, hero_image_url: defer until main text is stable.
# 6) Verify after Supabase restart: REST improves; above routes end 200 degraded not 500; main titles
#    survive auxiliary failures; grep confirms main path never uses articles_list_slim.
